Here you can find an alternative LaTeX template for revcolfis template.

      Usage:

You can use all the revtex4 advantages on the documents generated with \documentclass[articleUdeA]

To set the title in English and Spanish use:
       	    \titleEsEn{Español}{English}

To set the article abstracts use:
       	   \begin{resumen}
		{Aqui el resumén}
		{Here the abstract}
	   \end{resumen} 
if you dont want an abstrac, leave the space empty:
       	   \begin{resumen}
		{Aqui el resumén}
		{}
	   \end{resumen}

IMPORTANT: Instead of using \maketitle, use \mtitle

Any report of bug, comments and suggestion send to
